exercises.name: Forearm Side Plank Twists
exercises.description: A challenging core exercise that targets the obliques and improves rotational stability. Start in a forearm side plank position, then rotate your torso and reach your top arm under your body.

exercises.name: Lateral Plank Walks
exercises.description: A dynamic core exercise that targets the entire core while improving stability and coordination. Start in a plank position and walk laterally while maintaining proper form.

exercises.name: Plank Hops
exercises.description: An explosive core exercise that targets the entire core and improves power. Start in a plank position and hop your feet in and out while maintaining proper form.

exercises.name: Plank To Jump Squat
exercises.description: A full-body exercise that combines core strength with explosive leg power. Start in a plank position, then jump your feet to your hands and perform a jump squat.

exercises.name: Plank To Pushups
exercises.description: A compound exercise that targets the chest, shoulders, and core. Start in a plank position and perform pushups while maintaining proper form.

exercises.name: Plank Ups
exercises.description: A core exercise that targets the entire core and improves stability. Start in a plank position and alternate between forearm plank and high plank.

exercises.name: Plank With Reach Out
exercises.description: A core exercise that targets the entire core and improves stability. Start in a plank position and reach one arm out in front while maintaining proper form.

exercises.name: Plank With T Rotations
exercises.description: A core exercise that targets the obliques and improves rotational stability. Start in a plank position and rotate your torso to form a T-shape.

exercises.name: Plank
exercises.description: A fundamental core exercise that targets the entire core and improves stability. Start in a plank position and hold while maintaining proper form.

exercises.name: Reverse Plank
exercises.description: A core exercise that targets the posterior core and improves stability. Start in a reverse plank position and hold while maintaining proper form.

exercises.name: Side Plank Lat Pull
exercises.description: A core exercise that targets the obliques and latissimus dorsi. Start in a side plank position and perform lat pull movements.

exercises.name: Side Plank Leg Pull
exercises.description: A core exercise that targets the obliques and improves stability. Start in a side plank position and pull your leg up while maintaining proper form.

exercises.name: Side Plank Rotation With Kicks
exercises.description: A dynamic core exercise that targets the obliques and improves rotational stability. Start in a side plank position and perform rotations with kicks.

exercises.name: Side Plank Star
exercises.description: A challenging core exercise that targets the obliques, shoulders, and improves stability. Start in a side plank position, then lift your top leg and reach your top arm overhead to create a star shape.

exercises.name: Star Planks
exercises.description: A dynamic core exercise that targets the entire core and improves stability. Start in a plank position and perform star-shaped movements.

exercises.name: Straight Arm Plank Jacks
exercises.description: A dynamic core exercise that targets the entire core and improves cardiovascular fitness. Start in a plank position and perform jumping jack movements with your legs.
